{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-3","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 3","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Naučili ste da se tonski znaci uvek stavljaju na finalne vokale, a ne na inicijalne. Ako postoji više od jednog vokala u slogu, ovo su tri pravila za određivanje koji vokal dobija tonski znak:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Ako postoji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, tonski znak se postavlja na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako nema <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, ali postoje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">o</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">e</span>, akcent se stavlja na onaj koji je prisutan. Ova dva ne mogu biti zajedno u jednom konačnom slučaju.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Ako <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span> nastanu zajedno, znak tona se stavlja na drugi.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Zato što <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ai</span> ima <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, znak tona se postavlja na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lái</span>.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i dovrši slogove sa pravilnim toniranjem.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Zvuk izgovara slog <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bǎi</span>, koji ima početni <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> i finalnu složenu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ai</span>. Tonski znak se stavlja na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, prateći pravilo da ako postoji <span class=\"highlighted-text\">a</span>, dobija tonski znak.</p>\n<p>Ova silaba koristi treći ton, koji počinje usred, spušta se na niski nivo, a zatim ponovo raste.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-3"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"bǎi","feedback":"<p>Ova sloga spaja initial <span class=\"highlighted-text\">b</span> i final <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ai</span>, i koristi treći ton.</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-tone","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Lin Yating","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_compound_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":53.94,"finishTimestamp":54.8},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.86,"dialogue":{"text":"bǎi","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lin Yating","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.36,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/#zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","dashedName":"task-3","certification":"a1-professional-chinese","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","chapter":"zh-a1-chapter-pinyin","module":"zh-a1-module-initials-and-finals","block":"zh-a1-learn-compound-finals","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-4","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-compound-finals/task-2","id":"6621a7b1a89964984aa2fa6b","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-pr